    "answerText": "To set up your Clover Flex, follow these steps:\n\n1.  Plug a cable into the base of the device.\n2.  Route the cable through a channel on the base.\n3.  Connect the power cord to a power adapter.\n4.  Plug the power adapter into a grounded AC power outlet.\n5.  Open the top of the device to insert a roll of paper. The paper should be 40 mm or 1.5 inches.\n6.  Insert the paper into the device.\n7.  Press the power button to turn on the device.\n\nWhen charging the Clover Flex, do not put any metallic object between the charging area on the cradle and the Clover Flex. The charging cradle is designed only for the Clover Flex. Store in a dry location and clean with a dry cloth. Do not disassemble or modify the device.\n",
